itunes:title: Bret Weinstein and Yuri Deigin: Did Covid-19 leak From a Lab?
title: Bret Weinstein and Yuri Deigin: Did Covid-19 leak From a Lab?
description:
Yuri Deigin and Bret Weinstein Discuss the evidence for the SARS-CoV-2 lab-leak hypothesis. 
Find his Medium article here: https://medium.com/@yurideigin/lab-made-cov2-genealogy-through-the-lens-of-gain-of-function-research-f96dd7413748 

Like this content? Subscribe to the channel, like this video, follow us on twitter (@BretWeinstein, @ydeigin), and consider supporting me on Patreon or Paypal. 

Theme Music: Thank you to Martin Molin of Wintergatan for providing us the rights to use their excellent music. 

Support the show (https://www.patreon.com/bretweinstein)
